name: Kida Nedakh (Atlantis) Disney by YeiyeiArt
description:
Kida is a well-known Disney character from Atlantis. To create the Lora, a meticulously selected and refined DataSet was used to achieve a versatile and flexible model. So that it adapts perfectly to styles and models. It also works in 3D. Use the keyword “(KidaWaifu:1)” for greater precision, and I also recommend using the keywords “(strapless, navel, armlet, tribal skirt, tribal), (bangs), (makeup) to invoke her characteristic outfits. If you want to change her outfit, I recommend lowering the weight of the Lora between “1.0 - 0.5” for greater flexibility, try it out and have fun. Remember to leave a Review with an image if you liked it and comment!! HAVE FUN :D

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. Currently Rapunzel, Snow White, Merida, Cinderella, Pocahontas, Fa Mulan, Elsa, Anna, Tiana and Alice in Wonderland, Ariel, Aurora, Jasmine From the Princess Series ;D” Also u have The Bonus Series with: Nani Pelekai, Lifeguard (lilo & stitch). And Tinker bell, Jane Porter (Tarzan).

Restaurant Series: Ronald McDonald, Wendys

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. YeiYeiArt.

Or

THE NEW !! Villain Collection: Maleficent, Ursula.
